Class Description
AddRequest
Creates a request for the system to add a song to the user's personal library.
ArtistSearchStrategy
This class will handle the implementation for searching through he database of songs when the user wants to use any search command involving artists.
ArtistState
ArtistState represents the state in the browsing system where a user has selected an artist to explore.
BackRequest
BackRequest is the class that fulfills a request to move back to a higher catalogue in the user library.
Browser
Browser represents an instance where the user is looking to browse their personal collection.
BrowseRequest
Ths is the class that will handle all the requests to browse the databases both the personal and global
BrowseState
BrowseState is the interface for which all of the states implement in the subsystem.
CLI
Invoker class for CLI commands that handle requests that users make.
CollectionState
CollectionState is the state where the user has called the initial browse command, in this state, all of the artists in the user's library.
DefaultState
DefaultState is the state of the browser before a browse command is called.
ExitRequest
Allows for a request to be called for the user to exit the system.
HelpRequest
Creates a request when the user asks for help.
LibraryRequest
This class works as the command Interface for the command pattern we implemented for the Different types of requests a user can make
MMLS
MMLS class is the Muze Music Library System application
MusicLibrary
This is the receiver class that implements all of the required commands that the user can do as per the system requirements
RateRequest
Creates a rate request when the user wants to rate a song.
ReleaseSearchStrategy
This class will handle the implementation for searching through he database of songs when the user wants to use any search command involving releases.
ReleaseState
ReleaseState is the lowest level in the browse searching tree.
RemoveRequest
Creates a request when the user asks to remove a song from their library.
SearchRequest
Creates a request when the user wants to search the global music database.
SearchStrategy
This Interface acts as the communicator between the searchRequest and the different Stratgies that it can implement
SearchStrategyRequest
SearchStrategyRequest class is the Context for Strategy design pattern
SongSearchStrategy
This class will handle the implementation for searching through he database of songs when the user wants to use any search command involving songs.
